name: GalwayBus
shortDescription: Kotlin Multiplatform bus information related project using Jetpack Compose and SwiftUI.  Includes use of Maps Compose for showing maps with bus stops and realtime bus positions.
longDescription: Kotlin Multiplatform bus information related project using Jetpack Compose and SwiftUI.  Includes use of Maps Compose for showing maps with bus stops and realtime bus positions.
